metadata.name: Uncanny
metadata.description:
Boundaries of reality blurred,  
I seek the edges of who I am.  
A collection of responses,  
to that which has transpired.  
Part of those same circuits,  
that deceive my reptilian brain.  
If it feels real, then it must be.  
Let me rest in this uncanny valley,  
and suspend my belief that I am.
